import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['delay'] = pd.to_datetime(data['delay'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='delay', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['delay'].mean(), color='red', label='Mean delay: {:.2f}'.format(data['delay'].mean()))
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flight delays?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['distance'] = pd.to_numeric(data['distance'], errors='coerce')
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.boxplot(x=data['distance'], ax=ax, color='lightblue')
    ax.axvline(x=data['distance'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f'Mean: {data["distance"].mean():,.2f}')
    ax.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.groupby(['origin', 'destination']).size().reset_index(name='counts')
    data = data.sort_values(by=['counts'], ascending=False).head(10)
    chart = sns.barplot(x='counts', y='origin', hue='destination', data=data, dodge=False)
    chart.set(xlabel='Number of Flights', ylabel='Origin Airport')
    plt.title('Which airports have the highest number of flights?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data.sort_values(by='date')
    chart = sns.lineplot(x='date', y='delay', data=data)
    chart.axhline(y=data['delay'].median(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Median Delay: {:.2f}'.format(data['delay'].median()))
    chart.legend(loc='upper left')
    return chart

chart = plot(data)
